{"title":"These 7 incredible MacBook Prime Day deals won’t be around much longer","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2402692/these-7-incredible-macbook-prime-day-deals-wont-be-around-much-longer.html","date":1721232483000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>While we expected iPads, AirPods, and Apple Watches to get significant Prime Day discounts, the absolute star of the 48-hour sale is the Mac—specifically MacBooks. Amazon slashed the price of Apple’s popular MacBooks to lows never before seen, with savings of up to $700 on the newest models. Some specific configurations are sold out, but many are still available. These are the seven best deals remaining before the sale ends at midnight:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0B3BVWJ6Y/\" target=\"_blank\">13-inch MacBook Air (M2, 256GB, 8GB RAM)</a>: $799 ($200 off)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The M2 MacBook Air is already a great bargain at its usual $999 MSRP, but for $200 off, it’s a downright steal. You can get it in any color (midnight, silver, space gray, starlight), and with Apple’s latest design, it won’t feel like last year’s model.</p>\n\n\n<span></span><div><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0B3BVWJ6Y/\" target=\"_blank\">Save $200</a></div>\n\n\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CX23V2ZK/\" target=\"_blank\">13-inch MacBook Air (M3, 256GB, 8GB RAM):</a> $849 ($250 off with $50 coupon on page)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We take notice whenever a new MacBook is discounted by more than $100, but $250 off the entry-level Air is absolutely incredible. This is Apple’s newest model of MacBook with an M3 processor and the ability to connect two external displays with the laptop lid closed.</p>\n\n\n<span></span><div><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CX23V2ZK/\" target=\"_blank\">Save $250</a></div>\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/MacbookAirM3Mitternacht.jpg?quality=50&amp