 $1,749 ($250 off)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The M3 MacBook Pro is Apple’s newest addition to the lineup, with the best parts of the Pro machines—the incredible Liquid Retina XDR display and expansive array of ports—at a lower price with a low-end chip and less storage and memory. Even with that model being <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CM5JV268/\">discounted to $1,399</a>, we recommend this Prime Day sale instead, which bumps the RAM and the storage, and still get it at an incredible price.</p>\n\n\n<span></span><div><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CX1NXX6Y/\" target=\"_blank\">Save $250</a></div>\n\n\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CM5JV26D/\" target=\"_blank\">14-inch MacBook Pro (M3 Pro, 512GB, 16GB RAM)</a>: $1,699 ($300 off)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If speed is important, this step-up model is a steal for $300 off, even with half the storage. And you can get it in space black.</p>\n\n\n<span></span><div><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CM5JV26D/\" target=\"_blank\">Save $300</a></div>\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Macbook-Pro-14-M3-Styrplatta.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"MacBook Pro 14-inch\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Macbook-Pro-14-M3-Styrplatta.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 4032w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Macbook-Pro-14-M3-Styrplatta.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Macbook-Pro-14-M3-Styrplatta.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Macbook-Pro-14-M3-Styrplatta.jpg?resize=1200%2C900&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Macbook-Pro-14-M3-Styrplatta.jpg?resize=1536%2C1152&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Macbook-Pro-14-M3-Styrplatta.jpg?resize=2048%2C1536&amp;qualit